{"tid":2495672,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解你受過嘅傷害我要承受？","createTime":"2021-04-19T10:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T19:21:46.000Z","uid":397459,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9d15613b11df84ec5f4159f77c32e3849b3a38","tid":2495672,"uid":397459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"點解你受過嘅傷，你前度留低俾你嘅傷口，<br />\n我要承受。<br />\n我小心翼翼照顧住你既感受，<br />\n唔想你記住以前唔開心既回憶。<br />\n但你就做返一模一樣既嘢，<br />\n原來你講嘢冇句真，<br />\n原來你都唔係咁好。<br />\n你可唔可以負返男人嘅責任？<br />\n你保護自己就可以唔顧我都有受傷嘅風險。<br />\n係咪我對你太好乜都就晒你你就有恃無恐？<br />\n其實我係個好易受傷既人。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝你俾我睇清楚你<br />\n<br />\n愛一個上一課<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54f928c90e7e4e630b3a2498000e95399204007","tid":2495672,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過 無一個人想做壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係大家都唔想自己俾人再傷害"},{"pid":"fddb46dec5848a4f19cbdcdf8f3d07d85085a143","tid":2495672,"uid":397459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b54f928c90e7e4e630b3a2498000e95399204007","tid":2495672,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過 無一個人想做壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係大家都唔想自己俾人再傷害"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:30:07.000Z","msg":"唔想俾人傷害就要傷害人？<br />\n但我一直以來都安守本分俾足安全感佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361c1855d43373f8de1a22255c5984a5ab6b2c27","tid":2495672,"uid":127033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"講咁多 即係分左未？<br />\n未就依家分 唔好再廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679b41bcb67fda16b4c6119660c71c3de654f603","tid":2495672,"uid":52819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fddb46dec5848a4f19cbdcdf8f3d07d8508